	•	Validation timestamp
	•	Validation host
 
⸻
 
Common Failures
No Domain Controllers Returned
Potential Causes:
	•	Domain Controllers offline
	•	DNS failure
	•	Active Directory service failure
 
⸻
 
Go / No-Go Decision
