⸻
 
13. Systems Manager Readiness Validation
Objective
Validate Systems Manager functionality.
Domain remediation activities later in the recovery process depend heavily upon Systems Manager.
 
⸻
 
Validation Areas
Verify:
	•	Fleet Manager available
	•	Managed Instances visible
	•	Run Command operational
 
⸻
 
Validation Procedure
Execute:
hostname
