⸻
 
Expected Result
Command Success
 
⸻
 
Success Criteria
Systems Manager is operational and capable of supporting recovery operations.
 
⸻
 
14. DR Readiness Approval
The DR environment is considered ready only when:
	•	Active Directory validated
	•	DNS validated
	•	Systems Manager validated
	•	Required AWS services accessible
 
⸻
 
Final Go / No-Go Gate
If any readiness validation fails:
NO-GO
Recovery activities must not begin.
 
If all readiness validations succeed:
GO
Proceed to Part 2 – Domain Controller Recovery, DNS Validation, and FSx Recovery & Validation.

