# 65. Security Group Validation Framework

## Objective

Validate security group rules after recovery.

---

## Background

One of the most common DR failures occurs when Production CIDRs differ from DR CIDRs.

Examples:

```text
Production:
10.131.x.x

DR:
10.134.x.x
```

Security Groups copied directly from Production may not function correctly.

---

# Validation Process

```text
Production Rule
        ↓
CIDR Translation
        ↓
DR Rule
        ↓
Connectivity Test
```

---

## Validation Areas

Review:

### Ingress Rules

Validate:

- Source CIDRs
- Source Security Groups
- Port Requirements

---

